                            <div class="accord-content">
                                <p>
                                    <b>NO,</b> shoulder has many intraarticular structure and
                                    hence many pathologies like Idiopathic Adhesive
                                    capsulitis, Rotater cuff tear, PASTA Tear, PBSTA Tear,
                                    SLAP Tear, Bankart Tear, Hill Sach’s Lesion, Biceps
                                    Tendon tear, Rotater Cuff Arthropathy, Shoulder
                                    Osteoarthritis, Shoulder Synovitis and many more hence
                                    it requires detailed history taking, astute physical
                                    examination and advanced imaging technology.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!--End single accordion box-->
                        <!--Start single accordion box-->
                        <div class="accordion accordion-block">
